The '''Holy Children of Asrat''' were a group of orphaned children who were worshipped on [[Asrat]]. Secluded in their temple, they opposed the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]], so they were targeted by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] for assassination. When the Empire ordered [[Dengar/Legends|Dengar]] to eliminate them, he was enraged and left [[Imperial Assassin|Imperial service]] to become a [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]].

